<div class="paragraph">
<p>Which sender information is delivered depends on the <strong>warehouse</strong> that is saved for the order.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>dimensions</strong> are retrieved from the system, depending on which options were selected for the shipping package in the <strong>System » System settings » Orders » Shipping » Shipping packages</strong> menu.</p>
</div>
