<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can enter the dimensions within the shipping package or import them from the corresponding item settings (in plentymarkets 7 for each variation in the <strong>Settings</strong> tab, in plentymarkets 6 in the <strong>Base</strong> tab in the <strong>Length/Width/Height</strong> fields).</p>
</div>
<h3 id="_defining_shipping_groups_on_amazon" class="discrete">Defining shipping groups on Amazon</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In order to offer items on Amazon with the correct shipping method, a shipping group must be created on Amazon.
You can manage these shipping groups by using properties for each item.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>We recommend using a property of the type <strong>text</strong> or <strong>selection</strong>. Link the property to the field <strong>merchant_shipping_group_name</strong>.
Save the name of the shipping group you have created in your seller central as a value for the text or the selection of the item.
For further information on linking properties, refer to our <a href="/en/markets/amazon/amazon-setup#1400">manual</a>.</p>
</div>
